    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a premier balance of performance and reliability. This unit has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our high standards for mechanical excellence and aesthetic presentation. Boasting a refined interior and a proven service history, this vehicle represents a sophisticated investment for the discerning driver who values both substance and style. Experience the assurance of quality engineering and enduring value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
