      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. It runs great, looks awesome, and I\u2019ve taken really good care of it. Perfect for your daily commute or a weekend getaway! Come check it out\u2014you\u2019re gonna love how it drives!",
      "price": 29500.0,
